Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.52,0:01:31.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I think it's time you\Ntold us your thoughts about this case?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.79,0:01:33.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The current Kira is foolish and
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.02,0:01:36.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,his exchange with the Japanese task force\Nwas far too convenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Taking that into consideration... Kira is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.86,0:01:40.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,probably conspiring with the\NJapanese task force.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.43,0:01:42.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Conspiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:43.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If that's the case, then Kira is...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:46.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The new L...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.50,0:01:47.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.24,0:01:50.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:52.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. But even though I say\Nthat I'm serious,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.81,0:01:54.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only seven percent sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.48,0:02:00.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Commander Rester, we have to make\Nassumptions during investigations.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.25,0:02:03.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're wrong,\Nwe can just say we're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.33,0:02:14.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There have been fewer crimes\Nin Japan lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:16.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My dad told me that if\Nyou do something bad,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.00,0:02:19.13,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,your name will be posted on the internet
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.20,0:02:23.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- and Kira will kill you.\N- What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.27,0:02:25.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, if you don't tell us your name,\Nwe can't file a report.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.88,0:02:28.44,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break-!\NAnything but my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.48,0:02:31.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to post your names\Non the internet.
