Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.14,0:03:04.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will declare this right here!\NKira is justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.93,0:03:09.11,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,187)}Kira's Kingdom
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.82,0:03:16.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is absolutely true that I was appointed\Nby Kira as his spokesperson.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:20.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Some people may try to kill me\Nbecause of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.76,0:03:22.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I am prepared to risk my life
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.21,0:03:28.97,Death Note Signs/Titles LG,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,390)\fad(501,501)}New Japanese Task Force Headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira's Kingdom, huh? What a horrible title.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.93,0:03:27.33,Death Note Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,to spread Kira's word around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.04,0:03:29.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world's come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.87,0:03:35.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Persecuting Kira is an unforgivable act\Nand should be considered a crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.28,0:03:37.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We should really kill this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.31,0:03:40.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you see someone trying to find Kira,\Nwhether that person is a police officer,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, the president's press conference is about to begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.88,0:03:43.88,Death Note Dialogue alt,,0000,0000,0000,,a regular citizen, or a criminal, bring charges against them!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.82,0:03:47.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What could it be about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.26,0:03:50.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They said that it was\Nan announcement to the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.23,0:03:53.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're always watching TV, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.70,0:03:58.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We, the United States of America...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.57,0:04:03.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:08.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Accept Kira and will do nothing\Nto stand in his way...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.58,0:04:13.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is insane!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.45,0:04:18.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it! The United States has\Nbowed down to Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is he talking about-?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.22,0:04:22.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is he afraid of Kira?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.89,0:04:25.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Mr. President, explain this!\N- When was this decided?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.43,0:04:26.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Give us more details!\N- Explain yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.73,0:04:28.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,- Are you saying that Kira is justice?!\N- That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.86,0:04:31.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Justice-? I didn't say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.83,0:04:34.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But war no longer exists\Nbecause of Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.84,0:04:37.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Criminal organizations are in a state of ruin,\Nnot only in the United States,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.51,0:04:39.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,but around the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.11,0:04:44.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no mistake.\NWhoever defies Kira directly will be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:47.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We know that Kira does not\Nstand for justice, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.58,0:04:51.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As a country, we will not take\Nany actions to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.39,0:04:52.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,T-That's the same thing! You idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.02,0:04:54.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You just announced that\Nyou accepted Kira!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.32,0:04:55.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Please explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.62,0:04:56.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you running away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.69,0:04:58.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you really call yourself\Nthe leader of our country?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.19,0:05:00.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.40,0:05:04.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the U.S. we're talking about...\NIt's their president's word.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.83,0:05:07.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... I'd like to ask\Na serious question.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.80,0:05:09.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it all of a sudden, Matsuda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.47,0:05:11.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that you're\Nnot always serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.24,0:05:15.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In the depths of your heart,\Ndo you think that Kira is evil?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.51,0:05:16.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:17.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean, Matsuda?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:22.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly... I don't think\Nhe's completely evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you believe that Kira is justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.19,0:05:27.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:31.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think that Kira is fighting evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:36.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The world has definitely become\Na good place for people who live honestly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.97,0:05:38.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're wrong, Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.80,0:05:42.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,They're afraid of the carnage.\NIt's not true peace...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.81,0:05:45.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.91,0:05:50.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I understand the feelings\Nof those who call Kira a savior!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.11,0:05:52.41,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.48,0:05:54.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A weak person...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.22,0:05:59.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm a detective.\NI can't accept Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.82,0:06:03.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that and want\Nto catch him as a part of my job.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.29,0:06:08.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,My head's probably messed up for not\Nbeing able to completely denounce him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.53,0:06:12.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing wrong\Nwith you, Mr. Matsuda.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.80,0:06:16.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light, you too-?\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.27,0:06:20.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Kira probably knows that\Nwhat he's doing is evil...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.08,0:06:25.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll change the world even\Nif he becomes a martyr...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:28.55,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That is the form of justice\Nthat Kira has chosen...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.25,0:06:30.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably what Kira thinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.52,0:06:36.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't argue over\Nwhether Kira is good or evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.23,0:06:39.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We just have to catch Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.53,0:06:45.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kira is caught, he is evil.\NIf Kira rules the world, he is justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.01,0:06:54.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But the world is rapidly\Ncoming to Kira's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.18,0:06:57.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Soon Kira will be justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.92,0:07:02.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen to us?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:06.21,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We've been dissolved because\Nof that chicken of a president...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.12,0:07:10.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not even a chicken.\NHe's not even a maggot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.36,0:07:15.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.93,0:07:18.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that\Naccepting Kira can be good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:49.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You're alive-?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.60,0:07:54.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:00.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.34,0:08:01.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let him in.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.59,0:08:14.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome Mello....
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.49,0:08:15.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Throw down your gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.56,0:08:22.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, please put\Ndown your guns.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.47,0:08:25.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It is meaningless for\Nus to shed blood here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:29.64,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But Mello killed the others.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.01,0:08:31.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me repeat myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.61,0:08:35.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our goal is to catch Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.68,0:08:38.77,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, killing Mello\Nwill not benefit us.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.39,0:08:48.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have things gone as\Nyou planned, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.66,0:08:50.85,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You've heard from\NLidner, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.13,0:08:52.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,About the Second L...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.46,0:08:57.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've pretty much figured out who\NKira is because of everything you've done.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:00.73,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.80,0:09:05.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not your tool to\Nsolve your puzzles!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.38,0:09:10.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello, shoot me if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.78,0:09:16.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.45,0:09:19.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you shoot Near,\Nwe'll have no choice but to shoot you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.16,0:09:23.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What'll happen if you both die?\NOnly Kira will be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.23,0:09:28.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph...that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.33,0:09:33.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, I just came to retrieve\Nthe photograph you have of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.67,0:09:34.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.47,0:09:38.24,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the photograph.\NThere's only one and there are no copies.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.61,0:09:41.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've already dealt with everyone
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.80,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,who knows your face at Wammy's house,\Nand elsewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.35,0:09:46.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say I'm a hundred percent\Ncertain, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.05,0:09:49.71,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's safe to say you won't\Nbe killed by the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.22,0:09:54.52,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that all, Mello?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.63,0:09:59.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.81,0:10:13.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I...have no intention of working\Nwith you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.41,0:10:15.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.31,0:10:20.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But it'll upset me if you\Njust take my picture and leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.45,0:10:25.75,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The killer notebook...\NIt's a Shinigami's notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.99,0:10:28.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever touches it,\Ncan see a Shinigami.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.49,0:10:31.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's crazy--!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.36,0:10:33.06,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Who would believe that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.13,0:10:34.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I believe him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.70,0:10:38.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What good would it be for\NMello to tell a lie like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:43.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He would, at least tell a better lie,\Nor something that has some truth to it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.17,0:10:44.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Therefore, Shinigami really exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.84,0:10:50.30,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The notebook I had was one that belonged\Nto someone other than a Shinigami...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.11,0:10:54.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Also...there were fake rules within\Nthe rules written in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.72,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I can tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.30,0:11:10.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.67,0:11:12.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mello...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.41,0:11:20.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Which of us is going to get Kira first?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.94,0:11:22.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The race is on...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.98,0:11:25.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Our destination is one in the same.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.78,0:11:27.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting for you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.98,0:11:28.57,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.67,0:11:53.87,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,A fake rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.54,0:11:57.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from previous events,\Nthere's no doubt that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.01,0:12:00.50,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,the notebook can cause heart attacks\Nand control its victims, to a degree.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.58,0:12:02.74,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,As for burning or tearing the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.82,0:12:06.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The book still exists and\Nthere is no way to test it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In that case...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.66,0:12:16.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The fake rule is the rule
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.53,0:12:20.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that a person will die if he doesn't\Nwrite a name within thirteen days...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.01,0:12:24.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Gevanni.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.74,0:12:27.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Get me L.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:28.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.35,0:12:32.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from Near.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.52,0:12:34.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.42,0:12:36.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, we've caught Mello.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.75,0:12:39.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But he escaped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:42.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,However, we were able to interrogate\Nhim a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.39,0:12:45.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,He didn't escape.\NYou let him escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.03,0:12:46.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.20,0:12:49.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, he really did escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.07,0:12:53.69,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Mello said that there\Nis a Shinigami attached to the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you been able to\Nconfirm any such entity?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.01,0:13:01.81,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Shinigami do exist.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:06.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I kept it a secret because\NI didn't think that you'd believe me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.95,0:13:09.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like to talk to the Shinigami\Nabout some things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.39,0:13:12.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.79,0:13:15.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thing that bothers me\Nthe most is the fact that
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.39,0:13:19.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there is a fake rule among\Nthe rules written within the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.66,0:13:21.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.96,0:13:22.66,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.13,0:13:29.20,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L, Tell me what you think.\NWhich rule do you think is a fake?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:35.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,By elimination,\Nit would have to be the one
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.48,0:13:40.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,that requires the owner of the notebook\Nto write a name within 13 days, or die.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:43.88,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you'd say that.\NI think so too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.12,0:13:51.29,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinigami. Was there a fake rule among\Nthe rules written within the notebook?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:53.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there aren't any.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.06,0:13:57.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So there's a Shinigami there?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.37,0:13:58.92,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.63,0:14:00.76,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.80,0:14:03.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I pretty much get the picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.61,0:14:08.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, Kira is there and\Nhe's making the Shinigami lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.14,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This guy's amazing.\NHe got it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.75,0:14:18.58,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if the Shinigami is lying,\Nit doesn't mean anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:22.45,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No. It would mean that it was\Nmeaningless to detain Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.26,0:14:26.49,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the rule that a person has\Nto continue to write names is a fake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.63,0:14:30.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it makes it meaningless that\Nhe spent more than 13 days doing nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.90,0:14:34.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that's wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.07,0:14:37.47,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Light is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.84,0:14:42.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The Deputy Director confirmed that he didn't\Nhave a notebook and passed away...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.19,0:14:53.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, how about testing it\Nin this way?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.56,0:14:57.42,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will write Mello's name in the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.43,0:15:04.26,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Mello dies, and if\NI die 13 days later, Kira wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.57,0:15:06.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.97,0:15:08.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.30,0:15:09.53,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,So it's just a matter of\Nwinning or losing?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.94,0:15:14.43,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if testing the 13-day rule\Nbenefits the Kira investigation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.64,0:15:16.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,there shouldn't be any drawbacks.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.18,0:15:19.98,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I shall put my life on the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.68,0:15:24.95,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If I reject this offer on my own,\Nit'll give a bad impression...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.05,0:15:29.35,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait a moment.\NWe need to think about that suggestion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.06,0:15:32.99,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me your honest opinion.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.40,0:15:35.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's easy to say that\Nwe should honor human life
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.23,0:15:39.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,and we shouldn't do that,\Nbut I was the one who was confined.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.40,0:15:42.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's strange for me to\Nbe saying that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.77,0:15:43.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is awkward...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:45.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that Near should do\Nit if he wants to.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.91,0:15:47.97,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to see\Nthe Deputy Director avenged.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.24,0:15:52.54,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm against it. I don't believe\Nthat Kira is among us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,We shouldn't kill anyone\Nwith the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.22,0:15:59.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. We should follow\Nthe Deputy Director's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.35,0:16:01.62,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also against testing the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.66,0:16:07.79,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, we cannot allow you\Nto test the notebook.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.80,0:16:13.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you would say that...\NAnd lastly, one more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.10,0:16:16.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To the members of\Nthe Japanese Task force:
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.57,0:16:22.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Was there ever a time\Nthat Second L was thought to be Kira?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:28.94,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If you've listened to the conversation\Nand want to help my investigation...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.45,0:16:34.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Call the number\NI'm going to give you. I'll answer.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.26,0:16:38.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that Light could be Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.83,0:16:42.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I just don't want to think that... But...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.36,0:16:44.96,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,If the thirteen-day rule is fake...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.30,0:16:47.46,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,it's true that we can't say\Nthat he's innocent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.14,0:16:57.04,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near... I've got to kill him-!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.55,0:17:06.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.92,0:17:07.65,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.59,0:17:09.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I-ls this a prank?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.23,0:17:14.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I will read you a list of people that\NI'm going to punish tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.16,0:17:17.03,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Check it and make your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.93,0:17:23.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President, I am very grateful\Nthat you have sympathized with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.34,0:17:26.31,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But that isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The SPK is trying to catch me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.68,0:17:34.01,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to stop them immediately,\Nand disband them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.95,0:17:40.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,At the same time, I want you to\Nuse American police, the CIA, the FBI...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.39,0:17:43.32,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,And all other intelligence agencies...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.86,0:17:47.16,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,To find out where the SPK\Nmembers are hiding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.80,0:17:53.63,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me know immediately.\NI will tell you how to contact me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.70,0:17:59.00,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. President...it is your choice whether\Nor not you live a long life.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.71,0:18:01.11,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't forget that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.44,0:18:03.27,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.42,0:18:12.51,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Demegawa! Please wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.69,0:18:14.28,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you suddenly going to New York?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.36,0:18:17.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to crush an organization\Nthat's defying Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.66,0:18:18.68,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's going to be live!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.89,0:18:24.23,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,This is an order from Kira.\NI had a call from the President.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.47,0:18:28.40,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't even know\Nwhat I'm saying anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.84,0:18:30.33,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care about anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:35.37,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll get a 100 percent, no,\N120 percent viewer ratings--!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.58,0:18:40.17,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.65,0:18:42.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The age of Kira has come-!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.53,0:18:53.89,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The last L was suspicious of Light...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.66,0:18:59.10,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'll just be killed if he really is Kira and
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.40,0:19:01.93,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I say that we should investigate\Nhim again...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.74,0:19:04.36,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,The thirteen-day rule...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.94,0:19:06.70,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Aizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.48,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I've known you for a long time.\NI know what you're thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.31,0:19:15.91,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,You should do what you think is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.65,0:19:19.09,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I never trusted L to begin with.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.65,0:19:25.56,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm doing what I'm doing now because\NI want to work with you rather than Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:27.02,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Ide...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.46,0:19:31.59,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll contact Near without\Nletting Light know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.53,0:19:33.19,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,All right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:37.60,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure that no one knows\Nwhat you're doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.72,0:19:59.39,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...I want to believe that...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.46,0:20:01.83,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,you're not Kira...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.34,0:20:09.86,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Big trouble! Demegawa's on TV and...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.78,0:20:16.84,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,I, Demegawa, along with\Nmy comrades have finally...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.91,0:20:19.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,pinpointed the location of\Nand surrounded the hideout
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.45,0:20:23.38,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,of the evil organization that\Nis trying to catch our god, Kira.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.19,0:20:33.82,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now, they appear to be\Nhiding within this building!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.63,0:20:39.12,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Behold the power of the people!\NThe power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.80,0:20:45.07,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,When Near escapes,\NI'll write his name in the notebook...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.67,0:20:47.61,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Light...I'm going to do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.51,0:20:52.67,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Near, At this rate,\Nwe'll really be dragged out...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.28,0:20:55.15,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,L...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.78,0:20:57.22,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Near?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.95,0:21:01.25,Death Note Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this a plan by Mello to\Nfinish off the SPK?
